            <section class="prose mt-8">
              <h2>How to use the time calculator</h2>
              <h3>1. Add or subtract time</h3>
              <p>
                Use the <strong>Add / Subtract Time</strong> tab to total
                multiple time entries (for example, work shifts or tasks) or
                subtract several durations from the first one.
              </p>
              <ol>
